  * **조직:** [Ultralytics](https://www.ultralytics.com/)
  * **날짜:** 2024-09-27
  * **GitHub:** [Ultralytics 리포지토리](https://github.com/ultralytics/ultralytics)
  * **문서:** [YOLO11 Docs](https://docs.ultralytics.com/models/yolo11)



